
Frontend (app.js / UI Layer)
    ↓
FastAPI Route (main.py)
    Function: asa_task()
    Endpoint: POST /asa/{task}
    ↓
Task Dispatcher (web_wrapper.py)
    Function: run_web()
    ↓
Connection Manager (client.py)
    Function: connect_asa()
    - Establish SSH using Netmiko
    - Detect hostname
    - Detect outside interface
    ↓
Netmiko Library (External Module)
    Function: send_command()
    - Executes ASA CLI commands:

        show hostname
        show run interface | include nameif
        show route
        show interface outside
        show crypto ikev1 sa
        show crypto ipsec sa
        show run crypto map

    ↓
Discovery Logic (discovery.py)
    Function: discover_tunnels()
    - Parse CLI output using regex
    - Extract:
        * Crypto map name
        * Sequence number
        * Peer IP
    - Determine tunnel status (UP/DOWN)
    ↓
Generate Tunnel Table
    - CLI formatted output (print table)
    - OR return stdout to Web UI


